span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 229, 153);\">定了很多</span></span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 229, 153);\">@</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 229, 153);\">。</span></span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 229, 153);\">@&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 229, 153);\">家里人之前一直用国内的舒适达，结果牙齿变得更加敏感，国外的版本跟国内的使用感差别很大</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 229, 153);\">所以请勿用国内的价格进行比较。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/24606750/TB28QyTcXXXXXXuXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!24606750.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">北美家庭医生推荐牙膏，可以防止牙</span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">齿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">被来自酒精、水果、</span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">苏</span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">打水等中的酸性物</span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">质</span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">的腐</span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">蚀</span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 78, 167); line-height: 1.5;\">。加强加固牙</span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"color: rgb(103, 7