    <li title=\"Abtei\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">品牌:&nbsp;Abtei</li>\r\n    <li title=\"片剂\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">产品剂型:&nbsp;片剂</li>\r\n    <li title=\"28粒\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">规格（粒/袋/ml/g）:&nbsp;28粒</li>\r\n    <li title=\"德国\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">产地:&nbsp;德国</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 38px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">本品为膳食营养补充剂；本品不能代替药物；本品不宜超过推荐量或与同类营养补充剂同时食用</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/购物提示(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"463\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: left;\">宝贝名称： Abtei Knochenstark Calcium 600 + D3 Tabletten, 28 St</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: left;\">宝贝产自：德国</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: left;\">宝贝介绍：</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">Ab ca. 30 Jahren beginnt der altersbedingte Abbau der Knochenmasse. Daher ist es wichtig, fr&uuml;hzeitig etwas f&uuml;r die St&auml;rkung der Knochen zu tun.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDer lebensnotwendige Mineralstoff Calcium ist ein wichtiger Baustein des Knochenger&uuml;stes. Er ist wichtig f&uuml;r den Aufbau, den Erhalt, die Festigkeit und die St&auml;rkung der Knochen. Dar&uuml;ber hinaus ist Calcium wichtig f&uuml;r starke Z&auml;hne und die Funktion von Nerven und Muskeln.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDamit Calcium gut in die Knochen eingebaut werden kann, hilft dem K&ouml;rper der &quot;Calciumeinbauhelfer&quot; Vitamin D3. Dieser steuert die Calciumaufnahme und f&ouml;rdert die Einlagerung des Calciums in die Knochenstruktur.<span style=\"font-family: arial;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\nAuf eine ausreichende Versorgung mit Calcium durch die Nahrung sollte geachtet werden, da es laufend durch den<br />\r\nK&ouml;rper ausgeschieden wird.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAbtei Knochenstark Calcium 600 + D3 - wichtig f&uuml;r starke und feste Knochen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNahrungserg&auml;nzungsmittel mit Calcium und Vitamin D3.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">宝贝为骨骼关节营养补充，每片包含600毫克钙和5微克的维生素D3。钙是骨骼的重要组成部分，有助于使我们的骨骼强壮，30岁开始随着年龄的增长，必须及早开始定期摄入充足的钙和维生素D3以加强骨骼。此款宝贝非常安全，孕妇也可以食用。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">钙是骨骼生长和强化不可缺少的必要物质，维生素D3控制钙的吸收和钙在骨骼中的最佳储存量。能有效改善增强骨质密度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">钙:1、对骨骼构成很重要。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">2、对肌肉功能的发挥是必不可少的。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">3、对神经&nbsp; 脉冲信号在人体神经和细胞中的传递起着某种重要作用。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">4、补充钙质，挺拔体态，减轻经前状况，改善睡眠。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">维生素D3：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">促进钙磷吸收、骨骼钙化、骨和牙的正常发育，维持正常钙的代谢。保护视力,让眼睛不干涩。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">一天一次店家建议您在早上用餐或者晚上用餐的时候吃一片。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\"><img align=\"absmiddle\" src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/787990941/TB2q4AfaXXXXXa7XXXXXXXXXXXX-787990941.png\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">宝贝为骨骼关节营养补充，每片包含600毫克钙和5微克的维生素D3。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">钙是骨骼的重要组成部分，有助于使我们的骨骼强壮，30岁开始随着年龄的增长，必须及早开始定期摄入充足的钙和维生素D3以加强骨骼。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 255);\"><strong>此款宝贝非常安全，孕妇也可以食用。</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">钙是骨骼生长和强化不可缺少的必要物质，维生素D3控制钙的吸收和钙在骨骼中的最佳储存量。能有效改善增强骨质密度。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">钙:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1、对骨骼构成很重要。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">2、对肌肉功能的发挥是必不可少的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">3、对神经 脉冲信号在人体神经和细胞中的传递起着某种重要作用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">4、补充钙质，挺拔体态，减轻经前状况，改善睡眠。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">维生素D3：促进钙磷吸收、骨骼钙化、骨和牙的正常发育，维持正常钙的代谢。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18